        Snark tuner for my guitars
      </li>
      <li
        class="relative pl-7 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:bg-gray-300 before:rounded-full before:w-1.5 before:h-1.5 before:top-[calc(0.875em-0.1875em)] before:left-1"
      >
        Small tripod mic stand
      </li>
      <li
        class="relative pl-7 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:bg-gray-300 before:rounded-full before:w-1.5 before:h-1.5 before:top-[calc(0.875em-0.1875em)] before:left-1"
      >
        Shure A81WS large foam mic windscreen (use a circular piece of plastic
        to help install)
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black dark:text-white mb-2">
      DAW/Plugins
    </h3>
    <ul>
      <li
        class="relative pl-7 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:bg-gray-300 before:rounded-full before:w-1.5 before:h-1.5 before:top-[calc(0.875em-0.1875em)] before:left-1"
      >
        Logic Pro X (DAW)
      </li>
      <li
        class="relative pl-7 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:bg-gray-300 before:rounded-full before:w-1.5 before:h-1.5 before:top-[calc(0.875em-0.1875em)] before:left-1"
      >
        Melodyne 5 Essential
      </li>
      <li
        class="relative pl-7 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:bg-gray-300 before:rounded-full before:w-1.5 before:h-1.5 before:top-[calc(0.875em-0.1875em)] before:left-1"
      >
        Slate Digital - Fresh Air
      </li>
      <li
        class="relative pl-7 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:bg-gray-300 before:rounded-full before:w-1.5 before:h-1.5 before:top-[calc(0.875em-0.1875em)] before:left-1"
      >
        Valhalla Vintage Verb
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Default>
